The '''Sylo family''' was a family of farmers on [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]]. At the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the family had lived on the [[Sylo farm]] for ten generations, and used it to harvest [[tritacale]] and [[yot bean]]s.

As of [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], the family consisted of:

*[[Griggen Sylo]]
*[[Tashna Sylo]]
**[[Paxi Sylo]]
**Six older children

By the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]], the family had been forced to abandon their farm, and their fate after that is unknown.

